1
00:00:07,625 --> 00:00:09,025
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

2
00:01:39,745 --> 00:01:43,065
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
‎QUEEN CHU‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

3
00:01:43,705 --> 00:01:46,065
‎EPISODE TITLE

4
00:01:46,665 --> 00:01:48,025
INK AND BAMBOO SLIPS

5
00:01:48,105 --> 00:01:49,105
BROCADE AND SILK

6
00:01:49,945 --> 00:01:51,105
In the previous life,

7
00:01:51,185 --> 00:01:53,585
the Anping Rebellion
erupted 25 days later,

8
00:01:53,665 --> 00:01:55,785
on the very day of my wedding next month.

9
00:01:56,385 --> 00:01:58,985
Should the wedding have never taken place,

10
00:01:59,505 --> 00:02:05,105
could the two princes have survived
and the rebellion been avoided entirely?

11
00:02:06,705 --> 00:02:07,665
Next.

12
00:02:07,745 --> 00:02:09,505
Sir, I've only got some herbs.

13
00:02:09,584 --> 00:02:10,744
Keep the rhythm in mind.

14
00:02:10,825 --> 00:02:11,945
-Just like this.
-Next. Move quickly.

15
00:02:18,025 --> 00:02:19,545
It's him.

16
00:02:23,305 --> 00:02:24,145
Fu Jiu.

17
00:02:26,305 --> 00:02:27,505
Why haven't you returned to Yunzhong?

18
00:02:29,305 --> 00:02:32,465
I'm under the General's orders
to escort your dowry.

19
00:02:32,985 --> 00:02:34,625
I'll head back once the wedding is over.

20
00:02:35,225 --> 00:02:37,225
Can you take me away from here?

21
00:02:39,425 --> 00:02:40,465
Right now.

22
00:02:44,505 --> 00:02:46,305
I only take orders from the General.

23
00:02:59,905 --> 00:03:01,985
Are you in trouble?

24
00:03:13,385 --> 00:03:14,545
No.

25
00:03:24,905 --> 00:03:31,705
‎QINGYUN PAVILION

26
00:03:31,785 --> 00:03:33,665
I'm staying at the guesthouse.

27
00:03:33,745 --> 00:03:36,545
If you need anything, just let me know.

28
00:03:42,025 --> 00:03:44,625
Miss, what's come over you?

29
00:03:44,705 --> 00:03:46,185
His Highness favors you so much.

30
00:03:46,265 --> 00:03:47,385
Gifts piled mountain-high.

31
00:03:47,465 --> 00:03:48,705
The wedding is just days away.

32
00:03:48,785 --> 00:03:49,865
Why the sudden change of heart?

33
00:03:49,945 --> 00:03:52,345
If you miss the General,
we can always write to him.

34
00:03:52,425 --> 00:03:53,505
I have to go back.

35
00:03:55,825 --> 00:03:59,425
I need to see my father.

36
00:04:00,785 --> 00:04:03,145
I am surrounded by Xiao Xun's eyes.

37
00:04:03,665 --> 00:04:05,785
I must find a way out.

38
00:04:06,985 --> 00:04:11,105
Never again
will I let history repeat itself.

39
00:04:11,185 --> 00:04:14,865
GAOYANG COUNTY

40
00:04:26,505 --> 00:04:28,225
Xie Yanlai, going by the name Fu Jiu,

41
00:04:28,305 --> 00:04:31,465
is now in the Capital
as one of Chu Ling's retainers.

42
00:04:31,545 --> 00:04:34,105
My dear brother is truly something,

43
00:04:34,185 --> 00:04:36,385
trusted enough by the General

44
00:04:36,985 --> 00:04:39,105
to escort his beloved daughter's dowry.

45
00:04:39,705 --> 00:04:40,905
What of Chu Ling?

46
00:04:40,985 --> 00:04:43,385
Before a century-old lineage
like the Xie clan,

47
00:04:43,465 --> 00:04:45,065
he is but a lowly general.

48
00:04:45,145 --> 00:04:48,545
Your eldest sister is the Crown Princess,
with a son for the throne.

49
00:04:48,625 --> 00:04:51,185
-Your clout in the court--
-Watch your tongue.

50
00:04:51,265 --> 00:04:54,425
XIE YANFANG, PRIME MINISTER OF CHU

51
00:04:55,665 --> 00:04:59,185
Though my family
once had several grand chancellors,

52
00:04:59,705 --> 00:05:02,185
we remained outsiders
to the Capital's nobility.

53
00:05:02,785 --> 00:05:04,905
Five years ago,
I used my failing health as an excuse

54
00:05:04,985 --> 00:05:06,505
and moved back to Gaoyang,

55
00:05:07,465 --> 00:05:09,505
all to give His Majesty peace of mind.

56
00:05:10,625 --> 00:05:11,505
And yet you,

57
00:05:12,105 --> 00:05:15,745
after all this time at my side,
still haven't learned to hold your tongue.

58
00:05:16,945 --> 00:05:18,425
My apologies, sir.

59
00:05:18,505 --> 00:05:19,665
Please forgive me.

60
00:05:20,985 --> 00:05:25,185
I fear his spending too much time
with Chu Ling

61
00:05:25,745 --> 00:05:27,985
has swayed his loyalty.

62
00:05:28,945 --> 00:05:31,025
Five years without a firm hand,

63
00:05:31,545 --> 00:05:34,065
and even the most obedient
will start to forget themselves.

64
00:05:35,465 --> 00:05:39,785
Once he returns,
I'll dull his bite and clip his wings.

65
00:05:40,625 --> 00:05:41,865
He'll learn.

66
00:05:43,945 --> 00:05:48,145
My hound
never bites the hand that raised it.

67
00:05:48,225 --> 00:05:50,345
As for Xiao Xun…

68
00:05:51,505 --> 00:05:55,905
With his wedding so near,
we might as well drop in for a drink.

69
00:05:57,705 --> 00:06:00,985
Your Highness, our spies report
Xie Yanfang is readying his carriage

70
00:06:01,065 --> 00:06:02,425
and looks to be heading out.

71
00:06:02,505 --> 00:06:07,505
He retreated to Gaoyang
on the grounds of poor health

72
00:06:08,025 --> 00:06:09,105
five years ago,

73
00:06:09,705 --> 00:06:15,665
keeping himself
within easy reach of the Capital.

74
00:06:15,745 --> 00:06:18,065
When Chu Ling was exiled,

75
00:06:18,145 --> 00:06:19,785
the Xie family wasted no time
seizing what they could,

76
00:06:19,865 --> 00:06:22,905
planting their own people
throughout the ministries.

77
00:06:22,985 --> 00:06:26,025
Now, seeing the two princes
at each other's throats,

78
00:06:26,105 --> 00:06:28,065
are they looking to swoop in like us?

79
00:06:28,145 --> 00:06:30,065
Easier said

80
00:06:31,585 --> 00:06:32,945
than done.

81
00:06:33,865 --> 00:06:35,665
Tie Ying.

82
00:06:37,545 --> 00:06:39,625
There is something I cannot make sense of.

83
00:06:41,425 --> 00:06:45,665
Why the sudden frost from Zhao?

84
00:06:46,305 --> 00:06:49,585
Has the loose tongue of someone

85
00:06:51,345 --> 00:06:52,865
alerted her?

86
00:06:54,465 --> 00:06:56,705
My loyalty to you is absolute.

87
00:07:01,185 --> 00:07:02,345
Enough.

88
00:07:03,305 --> 00:07:04,145
Rise.

89
00:07:04,745 --> 00:07:06,505
I know where you stand.

90
00:07:07,665 --> 00:07:13,825
But given this sudden turn,
we can no longer afford to wait.

91
00:07:14,505 --> 00:07:17,945
Tomorrow, we'll use the Third Prince
to remove the Crown Prince.

92
00:07:18,025 --> 00:07:23,745
His fall will drive the other to revolt,
and I will be there to restore order.

93
00:07:23,825 --> 00:07:26,665
But Zhao is a wild card.

94
00:07:26,745 --> 00:07:29,745
The longer we wait, the greater the risk.

95
00:07:53,545 --> 00:07:55,425
Le. What's happening?

96
00:07:56,025 --> 00:07:57,185
The Third Prince
has turned on the Crown Prince

97
00:07:57,265 --> 00:07:58,825
and staged a coup.

98
00:07:59,585 --> 00:08:02,305
It was supposed to happen
on the wedding day next month.

99
00:08:02,825 --> 00:08:04,425
Why has it come early?

100
00:08:09,265 --> 00:08:11,225
His Highness orders your protection.

101
00:08:11,305 --> 00:08:14,545
Please stay in the Chu Mansion
until further notice.

102
00:08:14,625 --> 00:08:16,465
ANPING REBELLION - PAST LIFE

103
00:08:16,545 --> 00:08:19,385
-Where is Xun?
-His Highness orders your protection.

104
00:08:19,465 --> 00:08:21,745
Please stay in the Chu Mansion.

105
00:08:25,505 --> 00:08:28,825
It's starting exactly like the rebellion.

106
00:08:51,385 --> 00:08:54,865
His brother, Chu Lan,
poisoned the eldest imperial grandson

107
00:08:54,945 --> 00:08:56,345
in the first year of Anping.

108
00:08:57,865 --> 00:08:59,505
Miss, what's wrong?

109
00:08:59,585 --> 00:09:00,905
Let's run.

110
00:09:00,985 --> 00:09:03,585
Le, go fetch Fu Jiu from the guesthouse.

111
00:09:03,665 --> 00:09:04,705
What about you?

112
00:09:04,785 --> 00:09:06,145
I'm saving the imperial grandson.

113
00:09:06,225 --> 00:09:07,985
Miss, your life is what matters.

114
00:09:08,065 --> 00:09:09,705
Why worry about the imperial grandson now?

115
00:09:09,785 --> 00:09:12,025
If he truly dies by my uncle's hand,

116
00:09:12,105 --> 00:09:14,345
when the reckoning comes,
none of my family will be spared.

117
00:09:14,425 --> 00:09:16,105
Le, go.

118
00:09:16,185 --> 00:09:17,945
-Hurry up.
-Understood.

119
00:09:26,025 --> 00:09:29,665
If Uncle was truly the murderer,

120
00:09:30,225 --> 00:09:33,145
then wherever he is,
so is the imperial grandson.

121
00:09:44,745 --> 00:09:46,225
CHU LAN, CHU ZHAO'S UNCLE

122
00:09:46,305 --> 00:09:50,705
Turns out it was really him.

123
00:09:51,265 --> 00:09:54,145
He's been in Xiao Xun's pocket all along.

124
00:09:54,905 --> 00:09:58,065
So, the poisoning of the Crown Prince,
the seizure of the Third Prince,

125
00:09:58,145 --> 00:10:00,745
and the murder of the imperial grandson
were all Xiao Xun's doing.

126
00:10:01,265 --> 00:10:04,465
He was behind the rebellion
from the very start.

127
00:10:09,985 --> 00:10:12,785
IMPERIAL ANCESTRAL TEMPLE

128
00:10:12,865 --> 00:10:16,145
Your Highness, the army is assembled
and awaits your command.

129
00:10:16,225 --> 00:10:18,865
Take your death-sworn
to the Crown Prince's place

130
00:10:18,945 --> 00:10:21,425
and slaughter every last soul.

131
00:10:22,025 --> 00:10:23,465
Yes, Your Highness.

132
00:10:23,545 --> 00:10:26,185
Once our forces
breach the imperial palace,

133
00:10:26,265 --> 00:10:28,825
the throne will have a new master.

134
00:10:31,345 --> 00:10:33,265
The Third Prince
poisoned the Crown Prince,

135
00:10:33,345 --> 00:10:34,225
massacred the Eastern Palace,

136
00:10:34,305 --> 00:10:37,065
plotted against the late Emperor,
and raised a rebellion.

137
00:10:37,145 --> 00:10:39,305
His crimes demand death!

138
00:10:41,665 --> 00:10:43,065
Rest assured, Your Highness.

139
00:10:43,865 --> 00:10:47,785
I shall hold the throne for you.

140
00:10:54,745 --> 00:10:57,705
Don't be afraid. I am Chu Zhao,
daughter of the Guard General, Chu Ling.

141
00:10:57,785 --> 00:10:58,625
Follow me.

142
00:10:58,705 --> 00:11:00,025
Silence.

143
00:11:00,105 --> 00:11:01,985
Xiao Xun massacred the Eastern Palace.
His crimes are unforgivable.

144
00:11:02,065 --> 00:11:04,705
As his betrothed,
you are definitely complicit.

145
00:11:04,785 --> 00:11:06,265
Do not come here playing the savior!

146
00:11:06,345 --> 00:11:09,505
I am pledged to him,
but my family serves only the Crown.

147
00:11:10,105 --> 00:11:12,945
You came to Chu Mansion in your extremity
because you know this to be true.

148
00:11:13,025 --> 00:11:13,865
Am I right?

149
00:11:16,785 --> 00:11:19,185
His Majesty tasked me
to guard His Highness

150
00:11:19,705 --> 00:11:22,345
and find Chu Lan here if danger arose.

151
00:11:22,425 --> 00:11:24,785
But where is he now?

152
00:11:24,865 --> 00:11:26,025
My uncle has taken ill.

153
00:11:26,105 --> 00:11:27,745
He bade me to bring you out
before he drifted away.

154
00:11:29,945 --> 00:11:32,825
My father holds
His Majesty's absolute trust.

155
00:11:33,425 --> 00:11:37,505
Xiao Xun's men are closing in,
and we are defenseless here.

156
00:11:37,585 --> 00:11:40,305
To wait is to surrender to them.

157
00:11:41,065 --> 00:11:43,545
Our only chance is to break out now.

158
00:11:44,305 --> 00:11:47,825
If… it isn't safe here,

159
00:11:48,345 --> 00:11:49,785
where's left to go?

160
00:11:50,825 --> 00:11:53,665
What can you possibly do?

161
00:11:59,345 --> 00:12:01,145
We're going to Yunzhong.

162
00:12:02,745 --> 00:12:06,705
To find my father,
the Guard General, Chu Ling.

163
00:12:23,105 --> 00:12:24,145
Mr. Fu.

164
00:12:25,305 --> 00:12:26,305
Mr. Fu.

165
00:12:28,585 --> 00:12:29,425
Where is Chu Zhao?

166
00:12:29,505 --> 00:12:32,745
She was off to save the imperial grandson,
yet there is no sign of her.

167
00:12:32,825 --> 00:12:34,105
She must have fled.

168
00:12:35,825 --> 00:12:37,505
Everyone, come with me and find Chu Zhao.

169
00:12:37,585 --> 00:12:38,745
I'm coming too.

170
00:12:39,265 --> 00:12:42,025
Stay here. You'll only slow me down.

171
00:12:44,905 --> 00:12:47,305
‎CHU MANSION

172
00:12:51,465 --> 00:12:52,665
The Flame Decree.

173
00:12:56,225 --> 00:12:58,905
Have someone set it off in an hour.

174
00:12:59,425 --> 00:13:00,825
Let's go.

175
00:13:06,345 --> 00:13:09,265
EASTERN PALACE

176
00:13:15,985 --> 00:13:17,985
Your Highness, we have swept the area.

177
00:13:18,065 --> 00:13:19,345
There are no survivors.

178
00:13:20,025 --> 00:13:22,665
How is Zhao? What of the Chu Mansion?

179
00:13:22,745 --> 00:13:24,465
We have men stationed there.

180
00:13:28,665 --> 00:13:30,105
Your Highness,

181
00:13:31,145 --> 00:13:35,705
I hope you and Yu will be reunited

182
00:13:36,385 --> 00:13:38,145
with the Crown Prince soon.

183
00:13:46,465 --> 00:13:48,065
This is not Xiao Yu.

184
00:13:58,825 --> 00:13:59,745
QINGYUN PAVILION

185
00:14:10,425 --> 00:14:11,265
Please rest assured.

186
00:14:11,345 --> 00:14:13,545
My father sent an escort with the dowry.

187
00:14:13,625 --> 00:14:15,345
I've sent word for them to come for us.

188
00:14:15,425 --> 00:14:17,865
-Okay.
-Check over there!

189
00:14:17,945 --> 00:14:21,665
Le, please find Jiu.

190
00:14:22,265 --> 00:14:23,625
Back then,

191
00:14:24,225 --> 00:14:27,385
Chu Ling built the Longwei Army for me,

192
00:14:27,465 --> 00:14:29,585
with fire as the call.

193
00:14:30,425 --> 00:14:34,265
Only the Flame Decree
could command their blade.

194
00:14:34,985 --> 00:14:40,225
He promised me that as long as they stood,

195
00:14:41,225 --> 00:14:44,425
I would never be in danger.

196
00:14:45,025 --> 00:14:46,745
He broke his word.

197
00:14:50,825 --> 00:14:52,665
He broke it.

198
00:15:35,585 --> 00:15:37,865
Your Highness,
why didn't you just stay put?

199
00:15:44,665 --> 00:15:48,145
With all this chaos,
I was honestly terrified

200
00:15:48,945 --> 00:15:52,745
and trying to find Xun
when I happened to run into His Highness.

201
00:15:53,345 --> 00:15:54,985
Tie Ying, good timing.

202
00:15:55,585 --> 00:15:58,625
Help me escort him back to the palace.

203
00:15:58,705 --> 00:15:59,985
I see.

204
00:16:00,585 --> 00:16:02,985
I'll have someone
take you back to the mansion.

205
00:16:03,705 --> 00:16:05,385
You may entrust him to me.

206
00:16:08,705 --> 00:16:11,145
He is far too shaken to leave my side.

207
00:16:12,665 --> 00:16:13,825
Where is Xun?

208
00:16:17,265 --> 00:16:19,465
Perhaps we can wait for him here.

209
00:16:19,545 --> 00:16:21,465
I must insist that you hand him over.

210
00:16:31,825 --> 00:16:33,465
Give him to me right now.

211
00:17:52,785 --> 00:17:54,505
What took you so long?

212
00:18:03,905 --> 00:18:07,665
Chu Zhao, I'm taking you back to Yunzhong.

213
00:18:08,665 --> 00:18:10,345
-Fall back.
-Wait.

214
00:18:14,225 --> 00:18:16,465
My orders leave no room for waiting.

215
00:18:16,985 --> 00:18:22,305
The General's orders
are to bring you back alive.

216
00:18:23,825 --> 00:18:25,745
Zhao, are you leaving?

217
00:18:25,825 --> 00:18:28,265
Aren't you going to take me
to my grandfather?

218
00:18:32,985 --> 00:18:36,105
What's your relationship with Xie Yanfang?

219
00:18:38,865 --> 00:18:39,865
Tell me.

220
00:18:42,385 --> 00:18:43,785
What…

221
00:18:46,025 --> 00:18:47,025
is your connection?

222
00:18:50,385 --> 00:18:51,905
Why does it matter?

223
00:18:52,665 --> 00:18:56,425
He is Xiao Yu, the late Crown Prince's son
and the sole heir to the throne.

224
00:18:58,465 --> 00:19:00,905
Fu Jiu, you must protect him.

225
00:19:00,985 --> 00:19:04,145
I follow military orders, not yours.

226
00:19:09,825 --> 00:19:10,985
A large force is closing in.

227
00:19:13,905 --> 00:19:15,585
-What are you doing?
-My orders are to get you out.

228
00:19:16,185 --> 00:19:18,305
-No one else is my concern.
-What about him?

229
00:19:18,385 --> 00:19:21,345
If he is meant to survive, it will be so.

230
00:19:21,425 --> 00:19:24,905
If not, there is no point dying for him.

231
00:19:25,745 --> 00:19:27,945
-Stay here and keep him safe.
-Yes.

232
00:19:29,905 --> 00:19:31,065
Zhao!

233
00:19:36,625 --> 00:19:39,425
Back then, Jiu got me
out of here just like this.

234
00:19:43,785 --> 00:19:45,265
ANPING REBELLION - PAST LIFE

235
00:19:47,905 --> 00:19:49,785
Stop. Put me down.

236
00:19:49,865 --> 00:19:50,905
I have to find Xun.

237
00:19:50,985 --> 00:19:54,105
I am charged
with your safe return to Yunzhong.

238
00:19:55,785 --> 00:19:58,665
I am charged
with your safe return to Yunzhong.

239
00:20:00,185 --> 00:20:02,105
I cannot let Xiao Xun take the throne.

240
00:20:11,145 --> 00:20:12,905
Chu Zhao, have you lost your mind?

241
00:20:13,505 --> 00:20:15,025
-I have to go back.
-Not a chance!

242
00:20:17,025 --> 00:20:17,865
Move.

243
00:20:19,745 --> 00:20:23,665
Fu Jiu, you must keep me alive,
or you'll be disobeying orders.

244
00:20:56,865 --> 00:20:59,345
-This way. Hurry!
-Here!

245
00:21:00,745 --> 00:21:01,705
Zhao.

246
00:21:43,345 --> 00:21:47,145
NOBLE VIRTUE, ENDURING GRACE

247
00:21:50,545 --> 00:21:53,465
Follow me and protect His Majesty.

248
00:21:53,545 --> 00:21:54,625
-Yes!
-Yes!

249
00:22:04,465 --> 00:22:05,665
There are more of them coming.

250
00:22:06,185 --> 00:22:07,265
What do we do?

251
00:22:07,345 --> 00:22:08,345
‎Don't worry.

252
00:22:09,305 --> 00:22:11,825
I'll die before you do.

253
00:22:16,025 --> 00:22:19,265
‎Kill!

254
00:22:45,105 --> 00:22:46,745
He's here.

255
00:22:47,265 --> 00:22:50,425
By my order, comb the city.

256
00:22:50,505 --> 00:22:53,625
Anyone resembling the imperial grandson
is to be killed on sight.

257
00:22:53,705 --> 00:22:56,865
The rest of you,
follow me into the palace!

258
00:23:22,065 --> 00:23:23,145
Excuse me.

259
00:23:23,745 --> 00:23:25,145
Who set off the Flame Decree?

260
00:23:25,225 --> 00:23:26,425
I did.

261
00:23:26,505 --> 00:23:30,625
The Longwei Army has existed
for over a decade,

262
00:23:30,705 --> 00:23:32,745
yet this is the first time I have seen it.

263
00:23:33,825 --> 00:23:36,865
So my father commands
not only the frontier troops,

264
00:23:37,585 --> 00:23:39,425
but also this secret army.

265
00:23:41,705 --> 00:23:43,345
So this is the army

266
00:23:44,545 --> 00:23:45,465
he mentioned.

267
00:23:50,745 --> 00:23:51,665
This is the Flame Decree.

268
00:23:51,745 --> 00:23:53,865
It commands a secret army.

269
00:23:53,945 --> 00:23:55,745
The late Emperor
had me train them in secret,

270
00:23:55,825 --> 00:23:57,105
just for times like this.

271
00:23:58,305 --> 00:24:02,505
They will help you
protect the Capital and Zhao.

272
00:24:08,145 --> 00:24:13,385
With them on our side,
leaving here just got a little easier.

273
00:24:13,985 --> 00:24:18,345
Last time, Xiao Xun marched on the palace
and the decree was never set off.

274
00:24:18,425 --> 00:24:20,625
The army stayed unknown to anyone.

275
00:24:21,145 --> 00:24:25,985
But now, they are my hand
to play against his bid for the throne.

276
00:24:26,065 --> 00:24:27,745
-Scouts.
-Yes!

277
00:24:31,425 --> 00:24:33,025
Go and clear the path.

278
00:24:33,105 --> 00:24:34,545
Try to avoid the Lord of Xiaonan's men.

279
00:24:35,265 --> 00:24:38,025
The rest of you,
follow me out of the city now!

280
00:24:38,105 --> 00:24:38,945
-Yes!
-Yes!

281
00:24:39,025 --> 00:24:39,905
No, wait.

282
00:24:43,545 --> 00:24:46,745
With the army behind us,
there is no need to flee.

283
00:24:48,025 --> 00:24:48,865
Where are you going?

284
00:25:01,545 --> 00:25:03,025
To the palace.

285
00:25:08,225 --> 00:25:12,065
Your Majesty,
with both the princes fallen,

286
00:25:12,145 --> 00:25:15,305
the heir to the Lord of Xiaonan
is coming soon to protect Your Majesty.

287
00:25:15,385 --> 00:25:17,105
DENG YI, ATTENDANT CENSOR

288
00:25:17,185 --> 00:25:21,025
Your Majesty, you must act now.

289
00:25:21,105 --> 00:25:27,065
This brother of mine
was always the patient one.

290
00:25:27,145 --> 00:25:28,785
Yet now,

291
00:25:30,105 --> 00:25:33,145
even he reached his breaking point.

292
00:25:34,185 --> 00:25:35,665
Tell me,

293
00:25:36,185 --> 00:25:41,305
who is truly fit to inherit my throne?

294
00:25:42,385 --> 00:25:44,905
Your Majesty, is the one you have in mind

295
00:25:45,785 --> 00:25:49,145
the Lord of Xiaonan or his son?

296
00:25:59,545 --> 00:26:05,025
After all these years,
you still know me better than anyone.

297
00:26:06,865 --> 00:26:10,025
Go… and draft the decree.

298
00:26:11,905 --> 00:26:12,945
Yes, Your Majesty.

299
00:26:34,865 --> 00:26:37,025
We are escorting
His Highness back to the palace.

300
00:26:37,105 --> 00:26:38,065
Open the gates at once.

301
00:26:38,785 --> 00:26:39,945
He is an impostor.

302
00:26:40,625 --> 00:26:41,785
His life is forfeit.

303
00:26:41,865 --> 00:26:44,105
On my command, cut him down on sight!

304
00:27:02,625 --> 00:27:06,065
Your commander has committed treason
and been executed!

305
00:27:07,105 --> 00:27:10,345
Redeem yourselves now
and all will be forgiven.

306
00:27:10,945 --> 00:27:13,985
Those who resist will be slain!

307
00:27:40,305 --> 00:27:42,305
Can we win a head-on fight?

308
00:27:43,065 --> 00:27:44,705
The gates will fail.

309
00:27:45,305 --> 00:27:46,865
It's only a matter of time.

310
00:27:47,865 --> 00:27:51,265
The moment Xiao Xun enters the city,
the first one he'll kill is him.

311
00:27:52,025 --> 00:27:54,745
The second will be you.

312
00:27:59,505 --> 00:28:02,985
Was that really him who just charged in?

313
00:28:03,585 --> 00:28:04,465
Ram the gates.

314
00:28:15,425 --> 00:28:16,265
Is it worth it?

315
00:28:18,425 --> 00:28:19,585
Worth a try.

316
00:28:22,625 --> 00:28:23,505
Very well.

317
00:28:24,745 --> 00:28:29,745
We shall hold the gates as commanded,
even unto death.

318
00:28:38,505 --> 00:28:39,425
Jiu.

319
00:28:40,305 --> 00:28:41,385
Take care.

320
00:29:07,505 --> 00:29:11,065
As the General said,
if the gates fall, we are no soldiers.

321
00:29:11,785 --> 00:29:15,305
If we are to die today,
let it be at these very gates!

322
00:29:15,385 --> 00:29:17,465
-No retreat!
-No retreat!

323
00:29:17,545 --> 00:29:19,185
-No retreat!
-No retreat!

324
00:29:19,265 --> 00:29:21,065
-No retreat!
-No retreat!

325
00:29:21,145 --> 00:29:23,505
-No retreat!
-No retreat!

326
00:29:38,185 --> 00:29:40,025
GAOYANG COUNTY

327
00:29:40,105 --> 00:29:41,985
Xiao Xun is truly without mercy.

328
00:29:42,065 --> 00:29:44,865
The entire Eastern Palace
has been massacred.

329
00:29:44,945 --> 00:29:46,505
Even the Crown Princess and her son were…

330
00:29:50,665 --> 00:29:52,625
Nothing is more real

331
00:29:55,585 --> 00:29:57,505
than blade and blood.

332
00:29:59,785 --> 00:30:01,665
The throne of the State of Chu

333
00:30:02,385 --> 00:30:06,305
shall never belong to Xiao Xun.

334
00:30:11,265 --> 00:30:16,385
Du Qi, muster the troops
and head to the Capital.

335
00:30:22,545 --> 00:30:24,745
Your Highness, I have failed you.

336
00:30:25,465 --> 00:30:29,305
I was careless
to have underestimated Chu Ling.

337
00:30:30,865 --> 00:30:33,625
Her Ladyship took the imperial grandson.

338
00:30:38,465 --> 00:30:39,305
Zhao.

339
00:30:40,305 --> 00:30:42,185
You've found something out after all.

340
00:30:50,265 --> 00:30:53,185
Anyone entering unsummoned shall die.

341
00:30:53,785 --> 00:30:56,385
I am Chu Zhao, daughter of Chu Ling,
the Guard General of Yunzhong.

342
00:30:56,465 --> 00:30:59,145
I have escorted His Highness back
and request an audience.

343
00:31:08,105 --> 00:31:12,225
TAIJI HALL

344
00:31:33,785 --> 00:31:34,625
Deng Yi?

345
00:31:36,225 --> 00:31:37,905
You know me?

346
00:31:37,985 --> 00:31:41,825
You were the Grand Mentor,
the person Xiao Xun trusted most.

347
00:31:42,425 --> 00:31:44,305
Of course I do.

348
00:31:47,305 --> 00:31:48,585
It is plain to see

349
00:31:49,225 --> 00:31:51,825
Deng Yi must have had a hand
in the rebellion.

350
00:31:53,505 --> 00:31:58,505
You and I have met before.

351
00:32:15,905 --> 00:32:18,905
Greetings, Your Highness.

352
00:32:23,745 --> 00:32:27,185
His Majesty is unwell
and cannot receive you.

353
00:32:32,825 --> 00:32:35,665
Your brush tells quite a crooked tale.

354
00:32:36,545 --> 00:32:38,745
Shall I charge your clan

355
00:32:39,705 --> 00:32:43,425
with treason with my brush
for tonight's trespass?

356
00:32:44,825 --> 00:32:46,545
What did Xiao Xun promise you?

357
00:32:47,225 --> 00:32:50,745
The Nine Bestowments
or the first honors for backing his rise?

358
00:32:52,505 --> 00:32:54,385
The Crown Prince's heir stands before you.

359
00:32:55,305 --> 00:33:00,385
Which do you think
leaves a finer mark in history?

360
00:33:00,905 --> 00:33:04,425
Kingmaking for a usurper
or guiding a young emperor to glory?

361
00:33:06,985 --> 00:33:09,705
And do you believe
Xiao Xun, once enthroned,

362
00:33:09,785 --> 00:33:12,545
would spare a historian
who knows the truth

363
00:33:12,625 --> 00:33:13,905
of how he seized power?

364
00:33:17,105 --> 00:33:18,985
But if His Highness takes the throne,

365
00:33:19,065 --> 00:33:21,065
you will be
the founding pillar of his reign,

366
00:33:21,145 --> 00:33:22,865
first among all ministers,

367
00:33:22,945 --> 00:33:26,225
with every word of history yours to write.

368
00:33:40,225 --> 00:33:41,425
Miss Chu,

369
00:33:42,425 --> 00:33:45,745
please escort His Highness to the Emperor.

370
00:33:55,665 --> 00:33:58,545
TAIJI HALL

371
00:34:00,425 --> 00:34:02,625
-Your Highness.
-I am Yu.

372
00:34:03,545 --> 00:34:04,385
Alright.

373
00:34:04,905 --> 00:34:07,945
Yu, from now on,

374
00:34:08,585 --> 00:34:12,264
our lives are bound together.

375
00:34:14,065 --> 00:34:17,824
My father is the person
His Majesty trusted most.

376
00:34:18,425 --> 00:34:22,465
And I want to be that person for you.

377
00:34:23,065 --> 00:34:24,905
You will always be the one I trust most.

378
00:35:17,465 --> 00:35:18,305
Your Majesty,

379
00:35:18,385 --> 00:35:22,105
Chu Zhao, daughter of Chu Ling,
has escorted His Highness back.

380
00:35:27,065 --> 00:35:29,585
I, Chu Zhao, daughter of Chu Ling,
the Guard General of Yunzhong,

381
00:35:29,665 --> 00:35:31,145
pay my respects to Your Majesty.

382
00:35:37,425 --> 00:35:42,025
Like father, like daughter.

383
00:35:42,105 --> 00:35:46,905
Bold beyond measure
and utterly without restraint.

384
00:35:48,425 --> 00:35:52,225
Your Majesty, the trespass
was never my wish.

385
00:35:52,825 --> 00:35:55,625
Mr. Qi brought His Highness
to my place for refuge,

386
00:35:55,705 --> 00:35:58,265
and my father's men happened
to be in the Capital.

387
00:35:58,345 --> 00:35:59,185
In that dire hour,

388
00:35:59,265 --> 00:36:02,265
I mobilized the Longwei Army
to guard the throne

389
00:36:03,105 --> 00:36:06,025
and ensure the safe return
of His Highness.

390
00:36:08,985 --> 00:36:10,385
Rise.

391
00:36:23,065 --> 00:36:24,505
Grandfather.

392
00:36:36,425 --> 00:36:40,945
I sent him away to keep him safe.

393
00:36:42,025 --> 00:36:46,385
And now you bring him back
to this very danger.

394
00:36:46,465 --> 00:36:50,505
What is your intent?

395
00:36:51,225 --> 00:36:56,145
Your Majesty, Xiao Xun
plotted against the princes,

396
00:36:56,225 --> 00:37:00,105
hunted your grandson,
and harbors treason against Your Majesty.

397
00:37:00,185 --> 00:37:02,985
Though betrothed to him,

398
00:37:03,065 --> 00:37:05,625
I will not stand by
and watch a traitor run rampant.

399
00:37:08,505 --> 00:37:09,345
Imperial Physician!

400
00:37:13,905 --> 00:37:16,905
Do not be afraid. He will be fine.

401
00:37:21,185 --> 00:37:23,505
If His Majesty were to die now,

402
00:37:23,585 --> 00:37:28,305
not only would I fail to stop Xiao Xun,
but he would frame me for regicide.

403
00:37:28,385 --> 00:37:32,025
Everything I have fought for
would be lost.

404
00:37:35,185 --> 00:37:36,385
We can't hold much longer!

405
00:37:36,465 --> 00:37:38,705
Get Miss Chu out of here!

406
00:37:38,785 --> 00:37:41,265
With that tally, they won't stop you!

407
00:37:42,825 --> 00:37:44,425
Hold on!

408
00:37:44,505 --> 00:37:45,745
Stand firm!

409
00:37:50,625 --> 00:37:52,505
See?

410
00:37:53,745 --> 00:37:56,705
I am poisoned and will not see the dawn.

411
00:37:57,625 --> 00:38:01,705
The decree of succession is already drawn.

412
00:38:02,265 --> 00:38:03,785
By daybreak,

413
00:38:04,905 --> 00:38:07,825
Xiao Xun will be the new emperor.

414
00:38:09,825 --> 00:38:12,745
Deng Yi will escort you both to safety.

415
00:38:15,305 --> 00:38:16,225
Your Majesty,

416
00:38:16,745 --> 00:38:19,905
would you truly hand this realm over
to the Lord of Xiaonan and his son?

417
00:38:19,985 --> 00:38:24,025
Can a child of six hold the throne?

418
00:38:26,985 --> 00:38:27,825
Let it be.

419
00:38:28,825 --> 00:38:31,025
Now that it has come to this,

420
00:38:31,625 --> 00:38:35,425
as long as a Xiao sits upon the throne,

421
00:38:36,265 --> 00:38:42,225
I can meet my ancestors with a clear soul.

422
00:38:42,985 --> 00:38:44,305
But Your Majesty,

423
00:38:44,385 --> 00:38:47,705
if His Highness goes to the border,
what is my father to do?

424
00:38:48,785 --> 00:38:52,705
Carve out his own territory
and defy the new emperor

425
00:38:53,225 --> 00:38:55,065
just to protect him?

426
00:38:55,585 --> 00:39:01,825
The troops under your father's command
need not be involved.

427
00:39:02,505 --> 00:39:03,945
The Longwei Army,

428
00:39:04,025 --> 00:39:07,025
spread across the land,
is enough to keep him safe.

429
00:39:07,105 --> 00:39:08,065
Your Majesty,

430
00:39:08,825 --> 00:39:11,065
willing or not, my father

431
00:39:11,145 --> 00:39:13,505
will be seen as a threat
to the new emperor regardless.

432
00:39:14,105 --> 00:39:18,385
If you trust him
to keep your grandson safe at the border,

433
00:39:18,985 --> 00:39:20,665
why don't you believe

434
00:39:20,745 --> 00:39:23,185
that he can protect His Highness
holding the throne?

435
00:39:27,865 --> 00:39:31,225
The last thing your father would ever want

436
00:39:31,905 --> 00:39:35,225
is to hold this realm together for me.

437
00:39:48,625 --> 00:39:52,665
You have reminded me of something.

438
00:39:53,185 --> 00:39:56,825
If Xiao Xun insists on marrying you,

439
00:39:56,905 --> 00:40:00,905
your father would not stand against him,

440
00:40:00,985 --> 00:40:05,545
and his troops would become a threat.

441
00:40:05,625 --> 00:40:06,905
It seems

442
00:40:08,985 --> 00:40:09,985
I cannot let you leave either.

443
00:40:34,345 --> 00:40:37,425
As commanded, whoever kills Chu Zhao

444
00:40:38,025 --> 00:40:39,505
dies by my hand.

445
00:40:41,545 --> 00:40:42,425
Insolence!

446
00:40:42,945 --> 00:40:46,225
You would risk your entire clan
to commit such blatant treason?

447
00:40:48,385 --> 00:40:50,065
I would welcome it.

448
00:41:05,905 --> 00:41:08,345
-Go ahead.
-Then we die together!

449
00:41:08,425 --> 00:41:09,585
Jiu.

450
00:41:19,425 --> 00:41:22,385
Your Majesty, please let me
be your grandson's elder sister,

451
00:41:23,825 --> 00:41:25,065
the Grand Princess

452
00:41:26,585 --> 00:41:28,545
of the State of Chu,

453
00:41:32,185 --> 00:41:34,065
and help him

454
00:41:35,305 --> 00:41:36,825
hold the throne.

455
00:41:36,905 --> 00:41:38,065
What did you say?

456
00:41:38,145 --> 00:41:42,345
I know you and my father
were sworn brothers

457
00:41:42,425 --> 00:41:44,465
before you took the throne.

458
00:41:45,785 --> 00:41:49,825
My title as the Grand Princess
would make my father kin,

459
00:41:49,905 --> 00:41:51,425
not just a subject to your grandson.

460
00:41:52,265 --> 00:41:56,225
And the frontier troops
and the Longwei Army

461
00:41:57,025 --> 00:41:59,225
become guardians for us both.

462
00:42:02,505 --> 00:42:03,705
So,

463
00:42:04,905 --> 00:42:09,185
that is His Highness's greatest advantage
in holding the throne.

464
00:42:10,745 --> 00:42:12,865
I may be dying,

465
00:42:12,945 --> 00:42:19,265
but I've still got enough breath
to kill you and your father,

466
00:42:19,345 --> 00:42:22,385
a plague upon this throne.

467
00:42:22,465 --> 00:42:26,745
Then why not spend it
securing a future for the realm?

468
00:42:27,825 --> 00:42:31,585
Xiao Xun's ascension
would invite unrest and rebellion

469
00:42:31,665 --> 00:42:34,105
and even invasion
from the Northern Desert.

470
00:42:35,345 --> 00:42:36,585
By then,

471
00:42:37,185 --> 00:42:41,705
the people will be consumed by endless war
and everything will be lost.

472
00:42:42,665 --> 00:42:44,625
How will you ever be able

473
00:42:44,705 --> 00:42:49,865
to face your ancestors
with a clear conscience in the afterlife?

474
00:43:02,585 --> 00:43:04,225
The Grand Princess

475
00:43:05,825 --> 00:43:07,945
of the realm…

476
00:43:09,705 --> 00:43:10,985
Please rest assured.

477
00:43:11,505 --> 00:43:15,545
This title begins with me
and ends with me.

478
00:43:16,185 --> 00:43:18,465
So long as I hold it,

479
00:43:18,545 --> 00:43:21,665
I take no husband, and I bear no child.

480
00:43:21,745 --> 00:43:24,865
I yield my power to no one,

481
00:43:24,945 --> 00:43:26,585
and I shield no one with my shadow.

482
00:43:27,105 --> 00:43:31,545
Should I break this oath,
I shall be marked a traitor,

483
00:43:31,625 --> 00:43:34,145
and let everyone be my executioner.

484
00:43:35,625 --> 00:43:38,185
I can wield a blade against enemies

485
00:43:39,225 --> 00:43:42,825
and cut every tie that reaches
for the imperial seal.

486
00:43:44,185 --> 00:43:47,905
What I desire is for the annals
of history to record,

487
00:43:49,505 --> 00:43:52,065
"Chu Zhao, the Grand Princess
of the State of Chu,

488
00:43:52,145 --> 00:43:53,705
remained unwed for life.

489
00:43:55,225 --> 00:43:59,585
She rests beside her father,
Chu Ling, at the border."

490
00:44:05,665 --> 00:44:09,425
TAIJI HALL

491
00:44:22,385 --> 00:44:27,865
I, Xiao Xun, heir to the Lord of Xiaonan
request to attend upon Your Majesty!

492
00:45:06,225 --> 00:45:09,785
The Third Prince, Xiao Zhu,
committed treason, murdered his brother,

493
00:45:10,385 --> 00:45:12,585
and massacred the Capital
in a bid for the throne.

494
00:45:12,665 --> 00:45:14,425
This cannot go unpunished.

495
00:45:14,505 --> 00:45:16,865
He is stripped of his title
and reduced to commoner status,

496
00:45:16,945 --> 00:45:20,185
and his maternal clan,
the Zhao clan, meets extermination.

497
00:45:20,265 --> 00:45:23,825
Xiao Xun, heir to the Lord of Xiaonan,
defended the throne with distinction

498
00:45:23,905 --> 00:45:26,025
and honored the imperial line.

499
00:45:29,305 --> 00:45:30,585
Your Highness.

500
00:45:31,305 --> 00:45:32,585
Please receive the decree.

501
00:45:39,185 --> 00:45:43,865
We, the Xie clan, have come
to your aid, Your Majesty.

502
00:45:56,705 --> 00:45:57,665
It's him.

503
00:46:03,785 --> 00:46:07,305
The stars bring ill omens,
and traitors breed chaos.

504
00:46:07,385 --> 00:46:08,665
Both of my sons have fallen.

505
00:46:09,265 --> 00:46:11,665
It is by the valor and wit of Chu Zhao,
daughter of Chu Ling,

506
00:46:11,745 --> 00:46:16,865
who rode armed to deliver
the imperial grandson to safety,

507
00:46:16,945 --> 00:46:20,505
that the Xiao ancestral line endures.

508
00:46:20,585 --> 00:46:23,025
Chu Ling and I once shared
the dust and blood of battle

509
00:46:23,105 --> 00:46:26,145
and swore a brother's oath.

510
00:46:26,745 --> 00:46:28,825
For the eternal stability of the realm,

511
00:46:28,905 --> 00:46:31,425
I hereby pass the throne

512
00:46:35,225 --> 00:46:37,345
to my eldest imperial grandson, Xiao Yu.

513
00:46:43,865 --> 00:46:47,745
And I confer the title
of Grand Princess upon Chu Zhao.

514
00:46:47,825 --> 00:46:51,665
Her betrothal to Xiao Xun
is hereby severed.
